{"tid":347944,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"[Path of Exile 流亡黯道] 國際服 3.0 大更新","createTime":"2017-08-05T09:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T10:42:13.000Z","uid":75050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ad31f8c4b10be60051c19c18562dbead995a530","tid":347944,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:16:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://dvsgaming.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/3194224-trailer_pathofexile_falloforiath_20170213.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdvsgaming.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F3194224-trailer_pathofexile_falloforiath_20170213.jpg%3F&h=0cdc93e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/hkg_mocha\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fhkg_mocha&d=nQu%2BaJ7V9%2F1xxbMCRdAVA57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=36344ed2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/hkg_mocha</a><br />\n<br />\n新畫質、新特效、新地圖、新系統、新天賦、新技能<br />\n<br />\n新增重大內容:<br />\n-新增第五章到第十章<br />\n-移除殘酷跟無情難度, POE現在主線就是從第一章打到第十章.<br />\n-更新角色創造/選擇畫面<br />\n-新增萬神殿系統:<br />\n萬神殿系統讓你可以跟神族對抗, 你可以獵殺古神後利用他們些許的能力來增強自己.<br />\n在城鎮可以裝備不同的神族之魂來增強你的防禦能力.<br />\n一共有4個主神魂12個副神魂, 你一次可以同時開啟一個主神一個副神魂. 並且可以在城鎮切換.<br />\n這個系統是增強你各類防禦能力, 不是攻擊.<br />\n另外, 所有的神魂(4+12)都會在1-10章中取得, 但每個神魂都有1-3層進階能力可以解鎖. 這些解鎖的條件是在遊戲後期中的地圖裡打敗同樣的王.<br />\n-新增遊戲內&quot;幫助&quot;頁面, 裡面有介紹POE裡基礎的操作還有遊玩介紹.<br />\n-大幅度改善新手教學<br />\n-介面HUD更新, 來應對奧瑞亞的殞落的主題<br />\n-新增8個瓦爾地區(第五章).<br />\n-新增天賦樹計畫系統<br />\n-新增水光/特效畫面處裡<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=18966&amp;snA=108346&amp;tnum=31\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D18966%26snA%3D108346%26tnum%3D31&d=nQu%2BaJ7V9%2F1xxbMCRdAVA57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=1488c264\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=18966&amp;snA=108346&amp;tnum=31</a>"},{"pid":"679419beb1edcbeabecf29e03c74a99da3e7508a","tid":347944,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T10:39:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d9ec6cfa36ed70e3a66ece7bf5f4a1e4f5e13c2","tid":347944,"uid":106492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T10:42:13.000Z","msg":"偷偷留下正評"}]}